            <h1>Please Note:</h1>
            <p>The address and phone number for the Worldwide Church of God given for material are no longer valid for obtaining the material offered in booklets, magazines, telecast and radio broadcast.</p>
            <p>HWALibrary.com has all material offered on this site 100% free. You do not need to call or mail your requests, simply do a search for the material offered on our site.</p>
            <p>The Worldwide Church changed their name and beliefs after Mr. Armstrong's death.</p>
            <p>Visit our <a href="/cgi-bin/get/hwa.cgi?action=faq">FAQ</a> page for instructions on downloading audio and video files.</p>
